title: Shock Photo: Human Breast Milk Destroys Deadly Bacteria
text:
Shock Photo: Human Breast Milk Destroys Deadly Bacteria 'The future is breast milk' Infowars.com - February 8, 2017 Comments Image Credits: bule/Pixabay . 
An amazing photo shot last week shows the extraordinary effect human breast milk has on harmful pathogens. 
College student Vicky Greene uploaded a photo to Facebook Sunday depicting what happened when she applied breast milk to petri dishes filled with the M. Luteus bacteria. 
Greene added that “It also worked with E. coli and had a fairly good go at MRSA too.” NEWSLETTER SIGN UP Get the latest breaking news & specials from Alex Jones and the Infowars Crew. Related Articles
